breakingChangesNotes:
• The `ip` command no longer returns reputation information. Please use the `asm-get-asset-internet-exposure` command for asset information from Xpanse or the Xpanse Feed Integration.
  • The `domain` command no longer returns reputation information. Please use the `asm-get-asset-internet-exposure` command for asset information from Xpanse or the Xpanse Feed Integration.
Make sure to check and update any Playbooks/Scripts that use the above commands.
